Uh… Uh. we started talking. chatting.
and it was very intimate. very quickly.

16
00:02:07.722 --> 00:02:09.388
And I shared everything.

17
00:02:09.389 --> 00:02:10.474
We shared…

18
00:02:10.475 --> 00:02:12.351
- I mean. sexually we shared everything.
- Yeah.

19
00:02:12.352 --> 00:02:16.480
And emotionally…
And I told him so much about…

20
00:02:30.578 --> 00:02:31.870
Sanders.

21
