33
00:03:20.545 --> 00:03:24.340
Okay. So. this all started with. uh.
an online scam?

34
00:03:42.442 --> 00:03:44.109
Yeah. it's crazy here right now.

35
00:03:44.110 --> 00:03:47.237
I mean. it's not every day
