Hey.

48
00:04:45.505 --> 00:04:46.838
I'm Geri Soto.

49
00:04:46.839 --> 00:04:50.133
I'm a… I'm…
I'm a journalist for <i>The Margin</i>.

50
00:04:50.134 --> 00:04:51.385
Oh.

51
00:04:51.386 --> 00:04:52.678
- Well. I love <i>The Margin</i>.
- Oh.

52
00:04:52.679 --> 00:04:54.263
- Um. call me Joyce.
- Great.

53
00:04:54.264 --> 00:04:55.889
