But you know what? Even if I did.

68
00:05:39.934 --> 00:05:42.519
all collegiate business
is strictly confidential. so…

69
00:05:42.520 --> 00:05:43.646
Hmm.

70
00:05:45.106 --> 00:05:48.483
But I could really just. uh…
I would appreciate

71
