if we could just discuss the...

72
00:05:50.528 --> 00:05:53.655
Oh. If you'll excuse me.
I have an appointment.

73
00:05:53.656 --> 00:05:55.867
- Oh.
- Okay. It's okay.

74
00:05:59.245 --> 00:06:01.997
You really don't remember
th-this man that we're...

75
