that is game over for custody.</i>

129
00:10:11.998 --> 00:10:14.542
- Uh-huh.
- <i>You really need to lock in. okay?</i>

130
00:10:15.919 --> 00:10:19.504
Um… Oh. Oh. this is Hazel.

131
00:10:19.505 --> 00:10:21.506
- I gotta go. Okay. Okay.
- <i>Okay. let's talk later.</i>

132
00:10:21.507 --> 00:10:22.508
